      • stretch

        void stretch(double cx,
             double cy,
             double cz)
        Stretches an object along each axis independently.
        Parameters:
        cx - The factor by which to scale the object along the x-axis.
        cy - The factor by which to scale the object along the y-axis.
        cz - The factor by which to scale the object along the z-axis.
